# Read Rules First

Before any operation (analysis, file reads/edits, commands, or implementation), read relevant files in `.cursor/rules/` so current project guidance is applied.

## Required workflow
- Start each new task by listing `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`.
- Read all always-applied rules first.
- Read any scope-specific rules relevant to files or areas you will touch.
- If a new rule file appears during work, read it before continuing.

## Priority
- Follow `.cursor/rules` guidance unless it conflicts with higher-priority system/developer instructions.
